Name: Antaria Online
About the game: Antaria Online is a Cross-Platform MMORPG being developed with community feedback. After washing up on the shores of an unknown island, players must fight monsters and complete quests to advance. Join the fun as you grow from zero to hero! Currently the following is available for players: Adventurer Job Bandit Job Crusader Job Mounts PvE Zones - Monsters, quests, loot, and a hard level cap at level 50. The cap will raise as new zones are released. Hub City - A hub to access PvE zones and access things such as a bank, a premium shop, quest givers, and more. Crafting - Craft all kinds of neat stuff. Factions - Level up several different factions. Party - Join with up to 4 players to adventure together! Chat - Chat with other players!
